gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 131, Wizards 127
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeated the Wizards, 131-127. Victor Wembanyama led the way for the Spurs with 24 points, eight rebounds, four assists and six blocks, while Jeremy Sochan added 23 points, four rebounds and three assists in the victory. Marvin Bagley III tallied 21 points and a season-high 12 rebounds for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Spurs improve to 8-34 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 7-34.
